[20/12/2017 23:02:46] <font color="#00ffff">por favor?</font>
[20/12/2017 23:02:50] <font color="#00ffff">Es para San Pancracio.</font>
[20/12/2017 23:02:50] <font color="#ffffff">Tome.</font>
[20/12/2017 23:02:58] <font color="#ffffff">Gracias.</font>
[20/12/2017 23:03:00] <font color="#00ffff">¿Cuánto vale este?</font>
[20/12/2017 23:03:06] <font color="#ffffff">53 Pts.</font>
[20/12/2017 23:03:06] <font color="#00ffff">¡Caray!</font>
